{"tid":1524260,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太子黑警恐襲只係結果咋，唔好忽略埋個起因呀！","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:42:00.000Z","uid":161430,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a155963f24ef694fd1a04c6cd7b9ff4b397d7a5d","tid":1524260,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"起因竟然係因為<span style=\"color: red;\">有藍絲阿叔拎鐵鎚追住人去打</span>，於是港鐵報警<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Js31Zn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJs31Zn8.jpg&h=83f656f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但警察到場竟然係咁樣處理<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/sXnY1hQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXnY1hQ.jpg&h=0fbb0856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好blame the victim<br />\n仲有唔好比任何人有藉口話係示威者搞事先<br />\n根本冇爭拗既空間，<br />\n連事件起因都係因為藍絲阿叔拎鐵鎚打人在先"},{"pid":"a62ea61f3b0d9849a2d696324e8c71164d081dff","tid":1524260,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXnY1hQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXnY1hQ.jpg&h=abafa30f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ecf4bda85865447f991db2015b5c36f762c2c4a","tid":1524260,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028d3bfa0e8cb32479dff6cf18269a913d6c1549","tid":1524260,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike"